{"tid":921763,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Hugh Jackman開世界巡迴演唱會","createTime":"2018-11-29T23:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T05:54:21.000Z","uid":41343,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ae451250943d67028bb7e4dc17b42963a633c1","tid":921763,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:00:39.000Z","msg":"澳洲男星曉治積曼（Hugh Jackman）卸下「狼人」一角之後，今在IG宣布明年將舉辦個<br />\n人全球巡迴演出，演唱歌曲包括《大娛樂家》、《孤星淚》等電影和百老匯的熱門歌曲<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n曉治積曼是唱作俱佳的演員，演出舞台劇近20年，2004年以《The Boy from Oz》拿下東<br />\n尼獎音樂劇最佳男主角殊榮；2012年《孤星淚》在大銀幕首開金嗓，獲封金球獎影帝，<br />\n去年在《大娛樂家》又歌又舞，迷人嗓音累積不少「歌迷」，個人巡迴表演的國家、時間<br />\n目前還未有進一步資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181129/640_a38447932f998852b6e140b321052960.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181129%2F640_a38447932f998852b6e140b321052960.jpg&h=6e31002a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4174b87a0ded36f5a1296ceec0154c74de7e6208","tid":921763,"uid":189109,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:06:32.000Z","msg":"Who am I~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nI'm Wolverine~~~~~~~~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c175f68895d88d47da1f7dd39e0a857859a3bcdc","tid":921763,"uid":122985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T01:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ca4e4b1b82d9a964c039289d9ab98f7cbaa801","tid":921763,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"......."},{"pid":"464b74f1bcee758c119a93726fd15beed11ac280","tid":921763,"uid":27303,"like":8,"disli